    "help": {
      "topics": [
        {
          "id": "overview",
          "title": "Ocean Themes",
          "content": "# Ocean Themes\n\nA collection of five ocean-inspired color themes for Clubhouse.\n\n## Themes\n\n### Coral Reef (Light)\nWarm sandy whites with vibrant coral and turquoise accents — the colorful life of a tropical reef.\n\n### Tide Pool (Light)\nSea-glass greens and soft coastal tones. A tranquil palette inspired by sheltered rocky pools.\n\n### Pacific (Light)\nCool blue-grays stretching to the horizon. A calm, expansive palette like the open Pacific under overcast skies.\n\n### Deep Sea (Dark)\nDescend into the deep blue. Rich navy backgrounds with luminous bioluminescent accents of cyan and aqua.\n\n### Abyssal (Dark)\nThe darkest depths of the ocean. Near-black backgrounds with sparse, muted light — mysterious and immersive.\n\n## Usage\n\nInstall the plugin and select any Ocean Theme from **Settings > Appearance > Theme**."
        }
      ]
